    "Considerations": [
        "During system updates or patches, legitimate changes to the registry keys related to port monitors may occur. These changes can trigger alerts, but they are not indicative of malicious activity.",
        "When new printer drivers are installed or existing ones are updated, modifications to the registry keys under 'SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Print\\Monitors' are common. These legitimate changes can be mistaken for malicious actions.",
